data.description: 4 bed 3 bath pool home. It can easily be divided into 3/2 main home and 1/1 unit with its own separate entrance. Located just a few minutes from Hollywood Beach in the desirable Hollywood Hills neighborhood. NO association dues and short-term rental-friendly neighborhood. Close to all major highways and the international airport. The large yard has many fruit trees. New roof shingle sloped roof in 2022, AC 2019. Ready to move in or ready to be your blank canvas.
